nodes.text: Sleta Suke was a female Ortolan who was the daughter of the planet Orto's ambassador to Coruscant. After Suke became engaged, a lavish engagement party was held in her honor in the Ortolan embassy on Coruscant. However, Suke secretly wanted to run away with Trunks Bibo, the leader of the Lost Ones street gang, and during the party Bibo and his gang attempted to abduct Suke.
